  "summary": "TPS54331 controller (TI, SLVS839H datasheet, fixed 570 kHz, Vref=0.8V, Vin range 3.5-28V) chosen for 3x Iout headroom over 1A and well-documented design procedure. Component values derived from Section 8.2.2 (pages 15-19): inductor by Eq. 8 with Kind=0.3; output cap by Eq. 12; input cap per Section 8.2.2.4; feedback divider by Eq. 4. With R_top=10.0k and the in-stock R_bot=1.82k (the ideal 1.91k is not in inventory), Vout = 5.196V (3.9% above 5.000V). For exactly 5.000V, add a 1.91k 0603 1% resistor (e.g. Yageo RC0603FR-071K91L) and substitute R2.",
